{"word":"στερίσκω","slug":"στερίσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στερίσκω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:στερέω'><el>στερέω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><i>to deprive</i> of a thing, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be deprived of</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic<p/>"}]}